{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/defendnew.png?t=1734563611\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/Comp_2_3.gif?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Koboo</strong> draws inspiration from the <strong>difficult</strong> 2D souls-like combat from Dead Cells, the scale of Shadow of the Colossus and the <strong>enchanting world</strong> of Princess Mononoke. <strong>Death is no longer the end!</strong> Strategic builds, skillful positioning and correct timings will get your further in your next run so you can restore balance to the <strong>ancient ecosystem</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/arsenalnew.png?t=1734563611\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/Comp_2_5.gif?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize Your Build</strong> - Dual wield weapons that each have their own <strong>4 upgrades paths</strong> to suit your playstyle. Learn Animal Abilities which will powerup through <strong>branching upgrade paths</strong> making you even stronger by the end of your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/unlocknewest.png?t=1734563611\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/Comp_2_6.gif?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collectables Galore!</strong> - Collect flower seeds, catch bugs, meet fish and befriend the forest animals to unlock Favor. Use Favor in the shop to unlock new <strong>Weapons, Animal Abilities, Infusions, Relics and upgrades</strong> so your future runs will have even more variety!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">More Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Branching Paths</strong> - 7 worlds to explore each with their own enemies and final boss </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Specialize</strong> - Create a unique build by combining Weapon Upgrades, Animal Abilities, Relics and Weapon Infusions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collect</strong> - Go friendly fishing, catch bugs and plant your own garden after boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Secrets</strong> - Metroidvania inspired exploration to help you discover the secrets of the Ancient Forest... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Accessibility</strong> - Many accessibility and gameplay options </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Controls</strong> - Full controller support and control rebinding</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/koboodiscordbanner.jpg?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Koboo: The Tree Spirit</strong> wouldn't be possible without the incredible support of our amazing Kickstarter community. Their passion and constructive feedback continue to shape the game, making it even better than we ever dreamed! You can follow our development and talk to us live on <strong>Discord</strong> anytime, we will respond as soon as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Thank you! \u2764</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- Jerome and Simon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Jousting Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/f849c2bfe95f983cbd48990d5e0fbcb58b73c7fe.jpg"},{"name":"Fate Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/8b6ae2806c33e051ff9dfa2441325bea5e1853b2.jpg"},{"name":"Water in the Circuits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/f415479da83e165e1f523a6566ee24049c6b550f.jpg"},{"name":"Mildly Favorable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/74558acd67125df717175a4ab556e06477f58acf.jpg"},{"name":"Fairly Favorable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/8c28a1adbf0fb7ee5c7b5b2098ce028716498701.jpg"},{"name":"A Paw From Every Corner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/a8c5b2984cb063021bc52f5207063467e9c022be.jpg"},{"name":"One Step At A Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/6dbb99d98cc75c695378c3b9ce0a02777f1a3881.jpg"},{"name":"You Can Start Today","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/d6a4e7d7d61f7d15a486db69e08efe39cc473d51.jpg"},{"name":"The Back of your Hand","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/87b35cd555ee640ec5992416506837f05251a80b.jpg"},{"name":"How Hard Could This Be?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/718190/f6254c6faf509b02c3d18bba606c9093154d50cb.jpg"}],"total":32},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734563611","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/page.bg.jpg?t=1734563611","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/266bb5d97d7392de3c664527897dcfd43bf18975/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734563611","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/266bb5d97d7392de3c664527897dcfd43bf18975/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734563611","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>CONTENT ROADMAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/contentroadmapdec18.jpg?t=1734563611\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/defendnew.png?t=1734563611\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/Comp_2_3.gif?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Koboo</strong> draws inspiration from the <strong>difficult</strong> 2D souls-like combat from Dead Cells, the scale of Shadow of the Colossus and the <strong>enchanting world</strong> of Princess Mononoke. <strong>Death is no longer the end!</strong> Strategic builds, skillful positioning and correct timings will get your further in your next run so you can restore balance to the <strong>ancient ecosystem</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/arsenalnew.png?t=1734563611\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/Comp_2_5.gif?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize Your Build</strong> - Dual wield weapons that each have their own <strong>4 upgrades paths</strong> to suit your playstyle. Learn Animal Abilities which will powerup through <strong>branching upgrade paths</strong> making you even stronger by the end of your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/unlocknewest.png?t=1734563611\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/Comp_2_6.gif?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collectables Galore!</strong> - Collect flower seeds, catch bugs, meet fish and befriend the forest animals to unlock Favor. Use Favor in the shop to unlock new <strong>Weapons, Animal Abilities, Infusions, Relics and upgrades</strong> so your future runs will have even more variety!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">More Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Branching Paths</strong> - 7 worlds to explore each with their own enemies and final boss </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Specialize</strong> - Create a unique build by combining Weapon Upgrades, Animal Abilities, Relics and Weapon Infusions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Collect</strong> - Go friendly fishing, catch bugs and plant your own garden after boss fights </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Secrets</strong> - Metroidvania inspired exploration to help you discover the secrets of the Ancient Forest... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Accessibility</strong> - Many accessibility and gameplay options </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Controls</strong> - Full controller support and control rebinding</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/extras/koboodiscordbanner.jpg?t=1734563611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Koboo: The Tree Spirit</strong> wouldn't be possible without the incredible support of our amazing Kickstarter community. Their passion and constructive feedback continue to shape the game, making it even better than we ever dreamed! You can follow our development and talk to us live on <strong>Discord</strong> anytime, we will respond as soon as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Thank you! \u2764</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- Jerome and Simon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Jerome Labelle","Simon Labelle"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/718190/header.jpg?t=1734563611","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Copyright @ 2024 Honest Rogue Games. All rights reserved.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257049615,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257049615/movie480.mp4?t=1724690352","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257049615/movie_max.mp4?t=1724690352"},"name":"Koboo: The Tree Spirit - Launch Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257049615/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1724690352","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257049615/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1724690352","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257049615/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1724690352"}}],"name":"Koboo: The Tree Spirit","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_free_license":false,"option_description":"","option_text":"Koboo: The Tree Spirit - <span class=\"discount_original_price\">$14.99</span> $7.49 USD","packageid":208267,"percent_savings":0,"percent_savings_text":"-50% ","price_in_cents_with_discount":749}],"title":"Buy Koboo: The Tree Spirit"